lead_paragraph: Newcomer Chase Kalisz edged Olympic champion Ryan Lochte to register the top qualifying time in the men's 400 meters individual medley on Sunday and set up the first showdown of the U.S. Olympic Swim Trials.

headline.main: Lochte and Kalisz Line Up for First Showdown of U.S. Trials
